+        '',
+        'Alternative Agents',
+        '+------------+------------+-------------------------------------+',
+        '| Agent Type | Confidence | Reason                              |',
+        '+------------+------------+-------------------------------------+',
+        '| researcher |      60.0% | Alternative agent for researcher... |',
